---
import { getImage } from 'astro:assets';
import mockupSrc from '/src/assets/media-src/projects/web-dev/mark-conlan/mockup-mark-conlan.png';

const M = '/assets/media/projects/web-dev/mark-conlan';

const WIDTHS = [640, 960, 1280, 1920];
const [mockupAvif, mockupWebp] = await Promise.all([
  getImage({ src: mockupSrc, widths: WIDTHS, format: 'avif' }),
  getImage({ src: mockupSrc, widths: WIDTHS, format: 'webp' }),
]);
const mockupAvifSrcset = mockupAvif.srcSet.attribute;
const mockupWebpSrcset = mockupWebp.srcSet.attribute;
---

<section class="mc-project relative flex flex-col">
  <div class="mc-intro-layout">
    <aside class="mc-sticky">
      <header class="mc-headline">
        <h1 id="mark-conlan-title" class="project-title-reveal font-display m-0 uppercase">
          <span class="project-title-reveal__inner">Mark Conlan</span>
        </h1>
        <ul class="mc-tags" aria-label="Project tags">
          <li>Shopify</li>
          <li>Liquid</li>
          <li>E-commerce</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mc-meta" aria-label="Project details">
          <p><i>Client: </i>Mark Conlan</p>
          <p><i>Sector: </i>Illustration /painting / art</p>
          <p><i>Country: </i>Ireland</p>
          <p><i>Format: </i>Shopify e-commerce website</p>
          <p>
            <i>URL: </i>
            <a href="https://markconlan.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              markconlan.com
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>
    </aside>

    <div class="mc-main-flow">
      <figure class="mc-hero">
        <picture>
          <source type="image/avif" srcset={mockupAvifSrcset} sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 64vw, (min-width: 970px) calc(100vw - 24rem), calc(100vw - 2rem)" />
          <source type="image/webp" srcset={mockupWebpSrcset} sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 64vw, (min-width: 970px) calc(100vw - 24rem), calc(100vw - 2rem)" />
          <img src={`${M}/mockup-mark-conlan-960.png`} alt="Mark Conlan ecommerce mockup" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" />
        </picture>
      </figure>

      <div class="mc-study">
        <div class="mc-study-card masonry-reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0ms">
          <article class="mc-block">
            <h2 class="mc-block__title">The challenge</h2>
            <hr class="mc-block__rule" />
            <div class="mc-block__body">
              <p>
                Mark Conlan is an Irish illustrator with a growing catalog of originals, prints, and
                collections. He had a Squarespace site that did its job: clean, presentable, his work on
                display. But as his catalog grew, the cracks started showing. The e-commerce was too rigid
                to handle the way he actually sells. The gallery looked fine, but couldn't adapt to the
                specifics of each project. He needed a platform that could grow with his practice, not hold
                it back. So we moved to Shopify, and built everything around how he actually works.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="mc-block">
            <h2 class="mc-block__title">Responsibilities</h2>
            <hr class="mc-block__rule" />
            <div class="mc-block__body">
              <p>
                Shopify setup &amp; migration - Liquid theme customization - Masonry gallery development -
                Product &amp; collection architecture - Launch
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="mc-study-card masonry-reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 80ms">
          <h2 id="mark-built-title" class="mc-built-title font-display uppercase">What we built</h2>

          <article class="mc-block">
            <h3 class="mc-block__title">Custom portfolio gallery</h3>
            <hr class="mc-block__rule" />
            <div class="mc-block__body">
              <p>
                Squarespace's grid options couldn't handle the variety of Mark's formats. I built a
                masonry-style gallery in Liquid, 100% tailored to how his illustrations are meant to be seen:
                format-aware, flexible, and fully editable by Mark without touching code.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="mc-block">
            <h3 class="mc-block__title">E-commerce built to scale</h3>
            <hr class="mc-block__rule" />
            <div class="mc-block__body">
              <p>
                Product templates, structured collections, variant logic: everything was set up to handle a
                growing catalog cleanly. Adding new works, new series, or new product types doesn't require
                rebuilding anything.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="mc-block">
            <h3 class="mc-block__title">His store, his control</h3>
            <hr class="mc-block__rule" />
            <div class="mc-block__body">
              <p>
                One of the core goals was autonomy. Mark can now manage his entire catalog, update
                collections, and launch new pieces without depending on a developer. The back-end is as
                considered as the front.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="mc-showcase" aria-label="Mark Conlan storefront media">
        <div class="mc-showcase__media">
          <figure class="masonry-reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0ms">
            <video src="/media/videos/mark-conlan-2-web.mp4" aria-label="Mark Conlan storefront scroll" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata"></video>
          </figure>

          <figure class="masonry-reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 70ms">
            <video src="/media/videos/mark-conlan-1-web.mp4" poster={`${M}/mark-conlan-temp-960.avif`} aria-label="Mark Conlan product interaction" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata"></video>
          </figure>

          <figure class="masonry-reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 140ms">
            <iframe src="/mark-conlan-animated-mockup.html" title="Mark Conlan animated mockup" loading="lazy" allow="autoplay"></iframe>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import '../../scripts/masonry-reveal.ts';
</script>

<style>
  :global(.project-detail-page) > .mc-project {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: min(100%, 1680px);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 20px;
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
  }

  .mc-intro-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(18rem, 0.72fr) minmax(0, 1.58fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .mc-sticky {
    position: sticky;
    top: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .mc-headline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .mc-headline h1 {
    max-width: 10ch;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 7.4rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  .mc-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .mc-tags li {
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.42rem 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-family-display);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .mc-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    max-width: 31ch;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: var(--font-family-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .mc-meta p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mc-meta i {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .mc-meta a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .mc-main-flow {
    --mc-study-gap: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);

    display: flex;
    min-width: 0;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--mc-study-gap);
  }

  .mc-hero {
    margin: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }

  .mc-hero picture,
  .mc-hero img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .mc-study {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--mc-study-gap);
  }

  .mc-study-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    padding: clamp(1.4rem, 2.8vw, 2.4rem);
    background: var(--palette-white);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .mc-built-title {
    margin: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 1.5rem) 0 0;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 4.6rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  .mc-block__title {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-family-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.9vw, 1.7rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .mc-block__rule {
    width: 100%;
    height: 0;
    margin: clamp(0.8rem, 1.6vw, 1.2rem) 0 clamp(1.2rem, 2.6vw, 2rem);
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-primary) 26%, transparent);
  }

  .mc-block__body {
    display: flex;
    width: min(100%, 62ch);
    margin-left: auto;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: var(--font-family-body);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .mc-block__body p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .mc-showcase {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .mc-showcase__media {
    display: flex;
    min-width: 0;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--mc-study-gap);
  }

  .mc-showcase__media figure {
    margin: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--surface-muted);
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
    background: #f5efe8;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .mc-showcase__media video,
  .mc-showcase__media iframe {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .mc-showcase__media video {
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .mc-showcase__media iframe {
    height: clamp(640px, 88vh, 1120px);
    border: 0;
    background: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .mc-intro-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    }

    .mc-sticky {
      position: static;
    }

    .mc-headline h1 {
      max-width: none;
      font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 15vw, 4.8rem);
    }

    .mc-block__body {
      width: 100%;
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .mc-showcase__media iframe {
      height: min(82vh, 760px);
    }
  }
</style>
